summary: TL*THE CONTACT OWNS A 2009 DODGE JOURNEY.  THE CONTACT RECEIVED NOTIFICATION OF NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 14V373000 (AIR BAGS , ELECTRICAL SYSTEM) HOWEVER, THE PART TO DO THE REPAIR WAS UNAVAILABLE. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE MANUFACTURER EXCEEDED A REASONABLE AMOUNT OF TIME FOR THE RECALL REPAIR. THE CONTACT WAS CONCERNED FOR THEIR SAFETY. THE CONTACT HAD NOT EXPERIENCED A FAILURE.
